            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Cette liste contient des films comme <code>\"Vertigo\"</code> et des dates de sortie comme <code>1958</code>, mais il n'est pas clair quelle date appartient à quel film.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"movies = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Parasite&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"1958\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"2019\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"]\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"10\" endIndex=\"19\" /><option startIndex=\"37\" endIndex=\"38\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>\"Vertigo\"</code> suivi de <code>,</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Intro 2",
            "id": 88424,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Nous pouvons regrouper des éléments de données liés avec un <strong>tuple</strong>, comme dans <code>movie_tuples</code> ici, qui regroupe les noms de films et les dates de sortie ensemble.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"movies = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Parasite&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"1958\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"2019\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"movie_tuples = [(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"1958\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"), (\" /><text value=\"&quot;Parasite&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"2019\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")]\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"62\" endIndex=\"79\" /><option startIndex=\"79\" endIndex=\"80\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>(\"Vertigo\", 1958)</code> suivi de <code>,</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Tuples",
            "id": 88353,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p><strong>Les tuples</strong> nous aident à regrouper différents éléments de données qui vont ensemble, comme dans le tuple <code>vertigo_data</code> ici.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"vertigo_data = (\" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"1958\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(vertigo_data)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"12\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"print\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"('Vertigo', 1958)\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>vertigo_data</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Parentheses",
            "id": 88354,
